    "Attackers are using AI techniques to manipulate AI/ML systems, for example, trading/stock market manipulation, which can have serious consequences [27,107].",
    "This underscores the vulnerabilities inherent in AI systems, even advanced AI models.",
    "Robust security measures are therefore essential to mitigate the adversarial AI threat.",
    "As shown in Fig. 3 and previously in Table 6, adversarial AI attacks encompass a wide range of vectors, including data poisoning, evasion, model extraction, and property inference.",
    "This diversity makes it difficult to defend against such attacks comprehensively [5,13,64]."
